[http://www.ampedwireless.com/products/sr10000.html Product page] "L000033 RE:V2.2" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. The hardware is the same as the [[Amped Wireless R10000]] and is thus assumed to have 4MB Flash and 32MB RAM. The default SSID, according to the FCC label, is '''Amped_SR'''. The default PSK should be '''wireless'''.
